{"tid":945681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大政府宣布暫停在中國推廣旅遊業","createTime":"2018-12-18T05:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T05:59:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c7a71ac09756f287242a71ee453b1a5dd18328","tid":945681,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"華為副董事長孟晚舟12月1日於在加拿大被捕後，加拿大前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）及商人斯帕弗（Michael Spavor）亦被中國扣查，中加關係急轉直下。加拿大聯邦政府周一（17日）宣布，暫停在中國推廣旅遊業。<br />\n<br />\n加國旅遊組織Destination Canada表示：「在某些特殊情況下，例如發生地緣政治問題或悲劇性事件，繼續推廣旅遊業的話只會令聲譽受損。因此，決定暫停在中國推廣旅遊。」<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，加拿大汽車零部件製造商協會（Automotive Parts Manufacturers&rsquo;s Association）主席沃爾佩（Flavio Volpe）表示，由於孟晚舟被捕事件，多間中國汽車製造商，已擱置在加拿大擴充業務的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大旅遊部長趙美蘭（Melanie Joly）上周五（14日）亦宣布，推遲原定本周到中國出席中加旅遊年（Canada-China Year of Tourism）的閉幕活動，並聲稱是兩國的共同決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/272383/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%A5%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F272383%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A5%25AD&d=80JSO3C4DhQkSCqIxZi%2BV%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=daed1fcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/272383/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%A5%AD</a>"},{"pid":"717fba64185ecfc71c86febd5e029da615d5a338","tid":945681,"uid":191815,"like":